#######################
# MINT - daemon toolset
#   c[] ---skrp of MKRX
# a toolset providing a command-line-interface to managing a vast array of daemons across a network
# the nature of scraping work requires periodic monitoring of many nodes: over-time & many iterations & chronic
# https://ibin.co/38j1IoadTmGz.jpg
# TOOLSET #############
PING_PID  # active demons
SHUT      # kill MINION
PET       # pause MINION
CHIRP     # stdout MINION
HICC      # stderr MINION
KICK      # PID MINION
BURP      # MINION dump
URPP      # init MINION

REBIT     # update MASTER/HIT
UURP      # MINION HIT size
URPP      # MASTER MINION
SUMM      # birth MINION
PLUCK     # XS MINION
REIN      # bandwidth MINION
